&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;1.0.0 nonfatal user error&amp;gt; org.apache.openjpa.persistence.ArgumentException: An error occurred while parsing the query filter &quot;UPDATE Application a SET a.user = null WHERE a.user.id = :userId&quot;. Error message: Expression &quot;UPDATEVALUE&quot; requires at least one child.&lt;br/&gt;
